overview: After Jenna commits suicide in a hotel, she has to journey through the underworld to effect her release. Along the way she encounters one depraved act after another, meeting Janine as well as the King of Hades. This isn't heaven vs. hell. This is true purgatory...a dark, lush sexual dreamscape where any desire can produce both bitter sweet pain as well as unimaginable ecstasy.
title: Janine Loves Jenna
